mods.abstract: Two color window card (blue and red on brown) announcing the Grand Ole Opry stars Lester Flatt and the Osborne Brothers at the Louisa High School Gym on October 9. Poster features metal photoplates of Lester Flatt and Osborne Brothers. For additional information about this poster see http://cmfdigitization.cmf.int:2011/cdm/ref/collection/hatch3/id/28007.
